text: Tori Spelling Is 'Pregger Chic' in Two Bump-Hugging Dresses -- See the Pics! by Desiree Murphy 4:33 PM PST, February 17, 2017 Photo: Getty Images Tori Spelling is showing off her trendy maternity wear! The 43-year-old actress, who is expecting her fifth child , a baby boy, with husband Dean McDermott, took to Instagram on Friday, sharing a series of photos of herself modeling two new dresses, both which highlighted her growing belly. Styled by Seth Chernoff, Spelling wore a gorgeous green tie-dyed mini dress by Ronny Kobo with strappy Gucci heels in one of the cute pics. "Don't let pregnancy wear YOU! WEAR pregnancy!" she captioned it, using the hashtags "#dressthebump" and "#preggerchic." She also got clever with her fashion credits, writing, "Dress by @ronnykobo shoes by @gucci bump by @torispelling & @imdeanmcdermott." A post shared by Tori Spelling (@torispelling) on Feb 16, 2017 at 5:02pm PST The platinum blond beauty sported a printed Marc Jacobs dress in her second photo, pairing it with opaque black tights and bright-colored stilettos by Stuart Weitzman. But according to her caption, the pregnant star felt a little tired when it was time to shoot look #2. "When the chicness is just too much sometimes a pregger just needs to sit down!" she joked. "#hautepregger." A post shared by Tori Spelling (@torispelling) on Feb 17, 2017 at 1:42pm PST WATCH: Candy Spelling Throws Extravagant Bel-Air Baby Shower for Daughter Tori Following Past Estrangement Earlier this week, Spelling's mother, Candy Spelling, threw her a beautiful baby shower at the Hotel Bel-Air in Los Angeles, California. Complete with fresh flowers, baby blue velvet napkins and a moving train going around the table, the bash was a dreamy delight. Hear more in the video below! RELATED SLIDESHOW
